title: Looking for some friends! ^_^

embed.description: New streamer!! :D Streaming norms and testing stuff ~

body:
Hi guys I'm a brand new streamer looking to share some funny moments and a bit of knowledge. I usually play with a handful of people but I want to expand my pool of friends and hear what others have to say about stuff XD! I've been playing for about 2~3 years and I'm currently a plat 5 scrub. I main mid, supp and adc.

Stop by and say hello. Hopefully I'll see you guys on twitch (=^_^=)!

Note: I accidentally deleted the other thread LOL!
